<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AgriConnect - Home</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #2E7D32);
            /* min-height: 100vh; */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2E7D32, #4CAF50);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 40px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .header .emoji {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .feature {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature h3 {
            color: #2E7D32;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 18px 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #2E7D32);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .btn.secondary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #757575, #424242);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(117, 117, 117, 0.3);
        }

        .btn.secondary:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(117, 117, 117, 0.4);
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 30px 40px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #666;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <span class="emoji">üåæ</span>
            <h1>AgriConnect</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Bridging the gap between farmers and buyers</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="description">
                Welcome to AgriConnect - the premier platform connecting farmers directly with clients 
                in a seamless agricultural marketplace. Join thousands of users already growing their business with us.
            </p>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üöú</div>
                    <h3>For Farmers</h3>
                    <p>Sell your fresh produce directly to buyers and get better prices for your crops</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üè¢</div>
                    <h3>For Clients</h3>
                    <p>Source fresh, quality products directly from trusted local farmers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">ü§ù</div>
                    <h3>Direct Connection</h3>
                    <p>Skip the middleman and build lasting relationships in the agricultural community</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/register" class="btn">üå± Join Now</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn secondary">üîë Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 AgriConnect. Connecting agriculture communities worldwide.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>